-- Etihad to Open European Office in Manchester, Telegraph Says
-- B y   A n n e - S y l v a i n e   C h a s s a n y
-- 2012-04-29T09:16:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/etihad-to-open-european-office-in-manchester-telegraph-says.html
Etihad Airways PJSC, the Abu Dhabi-
based airline, is to open a European headquarters in Manchester,
which could lead to the creation of 300 jobs, the Sunday
Telegraph said, citing anonymous sources.  The airline will first set up a call center, creating about
160 jobs, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anne-Sylvaine Chassany in Paris at 
 achassany@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
